                # together so group them with a | and make them optional.
                (?:
                    (?:[-_\.]?dev[-_\.]?[0-9]*)?         # dev release
                    (?:\+[a-z0-9]+(?:[-_\.][a-z0-9]+)*)? # local
                    |

                # The compatible operator requires at least two digits in the
                # release segment.
